{"tid":853082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首：香港要1千萬人口　中聯辦：要5千萬人口　準特首：要1億人","createTime":"2018-10-08T10:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T12:07:56.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"498b7433a74caeea04ea692e60b3342ea32a3ce3","tid":853082,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:25:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001012080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001012080&d=tKnd3gROq%2ByaursSrS5Iik%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f9a2015c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001012080</a><br />\n<br />\n2007年06月15日<br />\n<br />\n香港特首曾蔭權(Donald Tsang)認為，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港應增加40%以上的人口，使人口數量達到1000萬</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n人口數量略低於700萬的香港，已經是地球上人口最稠密的地方之一。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_7bfda70d0100qszx.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sina.com.cn%2Fs%2Fblog_7bfda70d0100qszx.html&d=tKnd3gROq%2ByaursSrS5Iik%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=826225e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_7bfda70d0100qszx.html</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Paul Peng<br />\n<br />\n原載《信報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3）香港欲在中國取得更加重要的地位，應該擁有更多的人口。學國際政治的人都知道，在綜合國力的構成因素中，人口的多寡是一個十分重要的因素。比如，雖然以色列經濟、軍事、科技、教育等各個方面都十分先進，但由於其人口只有700餘萬（與香港大體相當），所以該國始終只是大國的棋子而成不了大國。中共建政後，中國很長一段時間都貧窮落後，但由於是世界第一人口大國，所以中國始終是國際政治中的一個大國。<br />\n <br />\n目前在中國境內，人口近億的廣東、四川、河南等人口大省始終在國家政治、經濟生活中佔有重要地位。香港搞&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;，要想在國家的政治、經濟運行中發揮更大作用，佔更大分量，從而為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港這&ldquo;一制&rdquo;爭取到更大的利益，需要香港擁有更多的人口。假如香港有5000萬人口，那麼中央政府在制定涉及香港的政策時，一定會更加慎重，更加尊重港人的意願。</strong></span>我相信這個淺顯的道理大家都會明白。近一點的例子，為什麼香港總是比澳門重要，除了經濟等因素外，其實最重要的因素還是香港有700多萬人口，澳門只有50多萬人口。目前香港本土人士的生育意願這麼低，要維持現有的人口規模已然不易，唯有靠移民或內地孕婦來港生子了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cc17162/statuses/110389382690779136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcc17162%2Fstatuses%2F110389382690779136&d=tKnd3gROq%2ByaursSrS5Iik%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=57b3a32e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cc17162/statuses/110389382690779136</a><br />\n<br />\n信報星期五paul peng身份: 中聯辦宣傳文體部長彭健恆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://plastichk.blogspot.com/2009/07/blog-post_22.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplastichk.blogspot.com%2F2009%2F07%2Fblog-post_22.html&d=tKnd3gROq%2ByaursSrS5Iik%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=a39b561e\" target=\"_blank\">http://plastichk.blogspot.com/2009/07/blog-post_22.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news_topic/nt_content.asp?sid=1805&amp;nt=np\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews_topic%2Fnt_content.asp%3Fsid%3D1805%26nt%3Dnp&d=tKnd3gROq%2ByaursSrS5Iik%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f1c97935\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews_topic%2Fnt_content.asp%3Fsid%3D1805%26nt%3Dnp&h=488fe8d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news_topic/nt_content.asp?sid=1805&amp;nt=np</a><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長唐英年接受本報專訪時，就描繪了一幅粵港融合的遠景。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>他認為，香港的出路，在於一國兩制《基本法》框架下的融合發展觀</strong></span>。朝着粵港融合的目標前進，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港的巿場規模可以由現在七百萬人口擴展至一億人口</strong></span>；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7333/3305964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7333%2F3305964&d=tKnd3gROq%2ByaursSrS5Iik%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=3cd5729f\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7333/3305964</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/08/13/98/5123888.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F98%2F5123888.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=45372322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為人工島在粵港澳大灣區的區位示意圖。香港中通社圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181005/628698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181005%2F628698&d=tKnd3gROq%2ByaursSrS5Iik%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=1544166e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181005%2F628698&h=85f4fa53\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181005/628698</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/video/20181004/480pix/1538660222_61d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fvideo%2F20181004%2F480pix%2F1538660222_61d5.jpg&h=4e9b412e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李先生表示，高鐵開通增加其來港意慾：「因為它就像我們的後花園一樣，在整個珠三角，沒有一個城市能比得上香港的服務、美食和購物。以後想來就來，因為隨著這麼方便的高鐵開通以後，我們曾經要做的訪港計劃是不需要了，因為隨時可以買到票就可以走，不像以前我們還要計劃『十一』、『五一』這樣。」內地遊客郭先生亦表示高鐵很方便，但因為大部分時間也在穿過山洞，看不到風景，感覺比較像乘地鐵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20151012/large/a1802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20151012%2Flarge%2Fa1802a.gif&h=efb74c72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bb9d785c307ee2c12074e010573bd87e2080e19","tid":853082,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04752278bd5bdcb9c900acf24763b041c314bfad","tid":853082,"uid":16731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:47:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88ae73aa46263a6781962c35a1023484cf7833a4","tid":853082,"uid":16731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79d6777c01daffdc4301bc032266f6fcc0cbe04d","tid":853082,"uid":2640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:53:17.000Z","msg":"1億人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c817f553278b732b3b9bdb42c21ce166bfe271a","tid":853082,"uid":106026,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"一億其實好少,建議加到13億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者索性俾香港政府接管成個支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70abcf4dca215d5c9401fc8f5f8268898e00f09f","tid":853082,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:56:51.000Z","msg":"笑撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22da4c4becfb164b5947b053e8d1da10b58ab7e","tid":853082,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"填晒成個香港塞2000萬人都唔得啦,仲5000萬 1億"},{"pid":"5f5e81b3cd71e79351152c42f30382a58a0981e2","tid":853082,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:00:18.000Z","msg":"將中國變做香港中國咪有13億人口囉"},{"pid":"d1212c17e7f11f5aa1acac607d23aec130e819f2","tid":853082,"uid":111616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"唐英年係話市場規模<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac7eedc919b5e20782a5308676cb1cf8a12062c","tid":853082,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:03:27.000Z","msg":"支持拆毀關口 <br />\n全中國都可以住<br />\n中國十三億垃圾自由進出香港<br />\n支持！"},{"pid":"346926edabfa5b388acad54fbea9dfe74beed506","tid":853082,"uid":150912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:04:38.000Z","msg":"5000萬人就會慎重考慮政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老母你地國家13億人你都冇尊重過啦"},{"pid":"e5065769ec113cb863937885804cd66089d0c30f","tid":853082,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy